        <div class="col-md-4 side-box">
          <%= mail_to "anakayoshi@seewelltolearn.org ", subject: "Vision Screening for My Child's School", class: "contact-button-school" do %>
            Bring Vision Screening to your school!
            <span>Contact us here.</span>
          <% end %>
          <h3>Won’t well-child checkups catch any vision problems?</h3>
          Unfortunately, not necessarily. We’ve screened over a million children in the last fifty years and we’ve caught vision issues that even well-child checks have missed. In fact, in one study, over 30 percent of the children who failed our high-tech vision screening and ended up needing glasses, had previously passed a routine screening at their pediatrician’s office. 
